com.rulescape.odmtest.api.core

Annotation Type RuleAppPath


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface RuleAppPath
    Annotation that identifies the ruleapp name for the test case. All test classes must have this annotation, or inherit it from a base test class.

      Required Elements

      The ruleapp name
